TMUX Keyboard Shortcuts: (indentation implies a sequence of shortcuts)

<C-a> v = vertical split
<C-a> " = horiz. split
<C-a> [hjkl] = move in panes (vim keys).
<C-a> <space> = next layout.

<C-a>i = join panes
<C-a>o = send panes
<C-a>u = break panes

<C-a> ` = copy (vim mode inside that)
        v = copy start selection
                <enter> = copy copy into tmux buffer
                <y> = copy into system clipboard
<C-a> p = paste from system
<C-a> ] = paste from tmux

<C-a> x = exit pane

<C-a> n = next window
<C-a> w = search windows
<C-a> c = new window
<C-a> , = rename window

<C-a> r = reload tmux conf

<C-t> (no prefix) = send prefix.
